    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, place the coconut cream sachet<span class=\"text-danger\">(s)</span> in a mug and cover with boiled water until fully submerged (this softens the naturally hard cream)</p>\r\n<p><strong>Blitz</strong> the onion, garlic and ginger in a food processor (or with a hand blender) until fine</p>\r\n<p><strong>Heat</strong> a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium heat with 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> (4 tbsp)</span> vegetable oil</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
