    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Add</strong> the blitzed ingredients and cook until softened and lightly golden brown (approx. 3-4 min), then add the star anise, cinnamon and bay leaves and cook for a further 30 seconds&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, mix the curry powder with 100ml <span class=\"text-danger\">(200ml)</span> water in a bowl</p>\r\n<p>Tip: Diluting the curry powder prevents it from clumping up whilst frying!</p>",
